<h2>@Model.GetName()</h2>
<p>Hunger: @Model.GetHunger()</p>
<p>Exhaustion: @Model.GetExhaustion()</p>
<p>Bored: @Model.GetBoredom()</p>
<p>Age: @Model.GetLifespan()</p>
<p>Is Hungry?: @Model.GetIsHungry()</p>
<p>Is Exhausted?: @Model.GetIsExhausted()</p>
<p>Is Bored?: @Model.GetIsBored()</p>
<p>Hunger Counter: @Model.GetHungerCounter()</p>
<p>Exhaustion Counter: @Model.GetExhaustionCounter()</p>
<p>Boredom Counter: @Model.GetBoredomCounter()</p>
